Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.40,0:02:09.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天天氣晴空萬里  將會是場最棒的運動會
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.62,0:02:17.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請用文武雙全的精神來激勵平日的學業吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.93,0:02:22.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「10月13日  山上的頭目」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.30,0:02:25.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來是選手宣誓
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.40,0:02:29.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,選手代表上前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.47,0:02:30.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.88,0:02:34.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宮  正式場合要加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.39,0:02:35.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.64,0:02:39.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師  我們會乘著運動員的新風
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.79,0:02:42.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.85,0:02:45.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.29,0:02:47.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.39,0:02:48.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宮…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.94,0:02:53.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天氣真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.06,0:02:56.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天下了一場大雨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.45,0:02:59.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就不用擔心了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.73,0:03:02.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要勤奮地補充水分哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.09,0:03:05.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有很多飲料  隨意喝哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.62,0:03:06.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.31,0:03:08.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.81,0:03:10.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宮  歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.70,0:03:12.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,執行委員的工作完成了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.99,0:03:14.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  已經好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.84,0:03:15.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.33,0:03:18.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  今天大家好好加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.10,0:03:20.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打倒白組哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.69,0:03:21.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.28,0:03:24.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會盡我所能努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.13,0:03:27.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是拖了大家後腿的話就對不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.67,0:03:29.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃要放鬆哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.30,0:03:31.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然的話是無法樂在其中的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.58,0:03:36.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  首先樂在其中是最主要的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.37,0:03:38.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  還真是游刃有餘呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.59,0:03:40.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣就想打倒白組
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.71,0:03:43.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要加倍奉還給你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.16,0:03:45.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目…  你又來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.23,0:03:47.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會輸的人是你哦  沙英
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.69,0:03:56.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙英學姐  要開心點…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.87,0:04:01.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油加油  紅組
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.87,0:04:05.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,努力努力  紅組
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.73,0:04:10.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在開始  出場比賽的學生請集合
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.24,0:04:12.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn細明體}{\b1}{\bord0}{\fs25}借東西比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.59,0:04:18.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃  加油
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.16,0:04:19.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.03,0:04:26.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狗!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.36,0:04:30.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有哪一位帶狗過來的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.86,0:04:33.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狗嗎  呀～  帶上我家的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.95,0:04:37.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由～乃～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.15,0:04:39.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn細明體}{\b1}{\bord0}{\fs25}{\1c&H0000FF&}障礙物賽跑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.99,0:04:54.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宮  那是終點  終點！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.54,0:04:56.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn細明體}{\b1}{\bord0}{\fs25}蜈蚣賽跑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.01,0:04:58.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一二一二一二…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.65,0:05:00.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  比起一二
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.72,0:05:02.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,One Two是不是更容易理解？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.24,0:05:08.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  一二就是因為說「一二」來配合才容易走哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.64,0:05:12.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在初中的時候是說「左右左右」的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.71,0:05:14.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  很累的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.84,0:05:16.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「嘿休～嘿休～」怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.08,0:05:19.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話就和轎夫似的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.65,0:05:26.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼都那樣了還不摔跤
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.58,0:05:28.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn細明體}{\b1}{\bord0}{\fs25}{\1c&H003346&}投籃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.48,0:05:33.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了  紅組明顯處於劣勢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.93,0:05:36.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙英學姐  我想到一個好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.33,0:05:37.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由由
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.26,0:05:38.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.14,0:05:44.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後面的球好多
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.45,0:05:45.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由由  挺住！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.69,0:05:53.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  居然輸了19分
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.60,0:05:55.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話下午必須要加油了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.89,0:05:58.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是這樣  才要好好吃午飯
